Anglo Platinum Expects to Meet Output Goal, Business Day Says, Citing CEO

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-06T05:26:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/anglo-platinum-expects-to-meet-output-goal-business-day-says-citing-ceo.html
Anglo Platinum Ltd. (AMS)  expects to meet
its annual production target of 2.6 million ounces of refined
platinum this year even after experiencing a “high level” of
stoppages during the first quarter, Business Day reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Neville Nicolau.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  